traffic.phaseplan

Class PretimedPhasePlan

  • java.lang.Object
    • traffic.phaseplan.PhasePlan
      • traffic.phaseplan.PretimedPhasePlan
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class PretimedPhasePlan
extends PhasePlan
    A concrete class encapsulating the algorithm for controlling the progression from phase to phase in a pretimed phase plan. Objects of this class may be created since the two abstract cycle methods of the parent class are implemented. A pretimed phase plan needs to know the various phases in the plan, their order and the time to spend in each.
    Author:
    (C) Neville Churcher
    See Also:
    PhasePlan, FullyActuatedPhasePlan, Serialized Form
